00063 void GenericDataHeaderWriter::WriteNameValParams(std::ofstream &os, GenericDataHeader &g)
00064 {
00065         ParameterNameValueTypeIt begin;
00066         ParameterNameValueTypeIt end;
00067         g.GetNameValIterators(begin, end);
00068         while(begin != end)
00069         {
00070                 FileOutput::WriteString16(os, begin->GetName());
00071                 MIMEValue mv = begin->GetMIMEValue();
00072                 u_int32_t sz;
00073                 const void* ptr = mv.GetValue(sz);
00074                 FileOutput::WriteBlob(os, ptr, sz);
00075                 FileOutput::WriteString16(os, begin->GetMIMEType());
00076                 begin++;
00077         }
00078 }

00085 void GenericDataHeaderWriter::WriteParentHdrs(std::ofstream &os, GenericDataHeader &g)
00086 {
00087         GenDataHdrVectorIt begin;
00088         GenDataHdrVectorIt end;
00089         g.GetParentIterators(begin, end);
00090         while(begin != end)
